description: Seti's Polish Boys is a hot, food truck and full-commercial kitchen in Cleveland.  Grilled sausage sandwiches, French fries and cold sodas complete our menu.Catering and special events are a large part of our business, if you know anyone needing our service please let us know. We enjoy what we do and appreciate our customers. We are available on the weekends for catering and outdoor events.  Message us here for details.
